tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE feedback_data (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_name VARCHAR(50),
  feedback_text TEXT,
  car_model VARCHAR(50),
  overall_rating INT,
  design_rating INT,
  performance_rating INT,
  safety_rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id UUID,
  car_model TEXT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE feedbacks (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  car_model VARCHAR(50),
  rating INT,
  comments TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  car_model VARCHAR(50),
  feedback_text TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerRatings (
  rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id INT,
  feature_id INT,
  rating_value INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
